text.content: We analyze IR images/videos from blades during production and operation to validate heating‑element installation. Temperature‑dependent acceptance criteria require dynamic filters.

text.plain_text: We analyze IR images/videos from blades during production and operation to validate heating‑element installation. Temperature‑dependent acceptance criteria require dynamic filters.

text.content: Complex acceptance criteria vary with ambient temperature; manual review is time‑consuming and inconsistent across shifts.
